1
00:00:00,610 --> 00:00:01,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-dah!</font>

2
00:00:01,990 --> 00:00:04,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I look terrifying?</font>

3
00:00:04,100 --> 00:00:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! You're so adorable, it's terrifying!</font>

4
00:00:09,340 --> 00:00:11,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks perfect on you, Doux!</font>

5
00:00:14,150 --> 00:00:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna wear it tomorrow 
at the Face Reveal Ceremony.</font>

6
00:00:18,110 --> 00:00:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the demon king's daughter, Doux!</font>

7
00:00:21,450 --> 00:00:23,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fear me!</font>

8
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek! How spooky!</font>

9
00:00:25,630 --> 00:00:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>N-No...</i></font>

10
00:00:27,220 --> 00:00:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted Lady Doux to have an outfit</i></font>

11
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that'd make her look 
terrifying and dignified...</i></font>

12
00:00:32,550 --> 00:00:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Vouche!</i></font>

13
00:00:32,690 --> 00:00:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}IN CHARGE OF THE OUTFIT
VOUCHE</font>

14
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE FACE REVEAL CEREMONY IS TOO LIVELY!!</font>

15
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The Face Reveal Ceremony Is Too Lively!!"</i></font>

16
00:02:14,270 --> 00:02:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

17
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I look okay?</font>

18
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All that happens at a Face Reveal Ceremony</font>

19
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is literally her showing her 
face and greeting the crowd.</font>

20
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not that simple!</font>

21
00:02:25,530 --> 00:02:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Face Reveal Ceremony determines</font>

22
00:02:27,570 --> 00:02:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if the next demon king is truly worthy 
of their position and our service!</font>

23
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what's determined there!</font>

24
00:02:33,690 --> 00:02:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if they aren't, some 
have even plotted mutinies</font>

25
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and assassinations!</font>

26
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux doesn't even know 
how to be a proper demon yet</font>

27
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so what do you think will happen?!</font>

28
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but she's not going 
to learn that by tomorrow.</font>

29
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just give up and deal with it.</font>

30
00:02:47,220 --> 00:02:49,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, there's still a way.</font>

31
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

32
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the speech manuscript I spent 
all night writing for Lady Doux!</font>

33
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's what you meant.</font>

34
00:02:59,490 --> 00:03:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I let Lady Doux handle 
her own speech, it'd be...</font>

35
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Doux grows up,</font>

36
00:03:05,010 --> 00:03:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux wants to go on field 
trips with everyone,</font>

37
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">make a pool made of sweets,</font>

38
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">lay in the sun with Papa,</font>

39
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have sports festivals, and sing songs!</font>

40
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:18,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how that'd go.</font>

41
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She wouldn't utter a single word 
befitting of the next demon king!</font>

42
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You stayed up all night,
 and it messed with your head.</font>

43
00:03:24,510 --> 00:03:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In order to make sure tomorrow's ceremony 
doesn't fail, I need to get this to her!</font>

44
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me.</font>

45
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux.</font>

46
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must talk to you about 
tomorrow's ceremony.</font>

47
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lady Doux seems more serious than usual.</i></font>

48
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is she doing?</i></font>

49
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is... could it be 
a speech manuscript?!</i></font>

50
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I had no idea she was writing one herself.</i></font>

51
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll just have to take it and 
swap it out with the one I wrote.</i></font>

52
00:03:55,580 --> 00:04:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But she's working so hard on writing 
it, so I shouldn't take it...</i></font>

53
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then again...</i></font>

54
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sister?</font>

55
00:04:04,690 --> 00:04:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes?</font>

56
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

57
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, uh!</font>

58
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Y-You look so serious writing 
that, so I was just curious...</font>

59
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux is writing all the stuff she's 
gonna say at the recital tomorrow.</font>

60
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, I see.</font>

61
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not a recital! And now it's becoming 
even more difficult to swap out!</i></font>

62
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:27,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

63
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A diary about me?</font>

64
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BIG SISTER JAHI DIARY!!</font>

65
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}WE DID A STEALING TRIAL TODAY!</font>

66
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We did a stealing trial today!</i></font>

67
00:04:39,730 --> 00:04:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I BROUGHT HIM MUSHROOMS!</font>

68
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I brought him mushrooms!</i></font>

69
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Big Sister taught me 
magic, and we played lots!</i></font>

70
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BIG SISTER TAUGHT ME MAGIC AND WE PLAYED LOTS!</font>

71
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sister.</font>

72
00:04:51,460 --> 00:04:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm terribly sorry, Lady Doux!</font>

73
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I read that without permission!</font>

74
00:04:55,370 --> 00:04:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay!</font>

75
00:04:56,720 --> 00:05:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been writing in that diary 
ever since I met you, Big Sister.</font>

76
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

77
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been writing in it so I</font>

78
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">don't forget all the things you 
taught me and can learn them!</font>

79
00:05:11,450 --> 00:05:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, see?</font>

80
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can draw magic circles 
without looking now!</font>

81
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kept working real hard, 
and now I learned how!</font>

82
00:05:22,620 --> 00:05:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best tomorrow, 
so just watch me, okay?</font>

83
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux...</font>

84
00:05:44,610 --> 00:05:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will now start the 
Face Reveal Ceremony.</font>

85
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait patiently to see and hear the words 
of Lady Doux, our next demon king!</font>

86
00:06:07,540 --> 00:06:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's finally time, Dahaka.</font>

87
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is, darling.</font>

88
00:06:11,650 --> 00:06:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, just look how magnificent she looks.</font>

89
00:06:15,620 --> 00:06:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's finally begun!</i></font>

90
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You're still worried?</font>

91
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I'm the most anxious right now.</font>

92
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I never got to give 
her the manuscript.</font>

93
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But!</font>

94
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no regrets.</font>

95
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All that's left is for me to 
believe and watch over her.</font>

96
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:42,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the demon king's daughter, Doux!</font>

97
00:06:42,540 --> 00:06:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh!</font>

98
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone!</font>

99
00:06:51,170 --> 00:06:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Um...</font>

100
00:06:53,930 --> 00:06:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh... Hm?</font>

101
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was I supposed to say again?</font>

102
00:07:01,060 --> 00:07:03,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning!</font>

103
00:07:03,460 --> 00:07:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning!</font>

104
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's definitely a greeting 
only Doux could do!</font>

105
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How lovely.</font>

106
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux!</font>

107
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Doux's Dream."</font>

108
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:27,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"When Doux grows up, Doux 
wants to conquer the world!"</font>

109
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

110
00:07:28,610 --> 00:07:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>D-Did Lady Doux actually just 
say "conquer the world"?</i></font>

111
00:07:33,090 --> 00:07:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Because Papa told me that 
conquering the world is amazing</font>

112
00:07:36,650 --> 00:07:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we'll make everyone 
in the world friends!"</font>

113
00:07:40,770 --> 00:07:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh?</font>

114
00:07:41,850 --> 00:07:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"But I need to become a full-fledged 
demon to do that, so Doux is studying!</font>

115
00:07:49,230 --> 00:07:53,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so I'm gonna show everyone!"</font>

116
00:07:53,490 --> 00:07:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

117
00:07:54,350 --> 00:07:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please make some space.</font>

118
00:07:55,470 --> 00:07:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please make some space!</font>

119
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux, we're ready!</font>

120
00:08:02,290 --> 00:08:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

121
00:08:04,130 --> 00:08:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then...</font>

122
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:08,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just watch!</font>

123
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

124
00:08:13,460 --> 00:08:15,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That spell is...</font>

125
00:08:17,770 --> 00:08:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boom!</font>

126
00:08:28,350 --> 00:08:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

127
00:08:29,860 --> 00:08:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boom!</font>

128
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TREE</font>

129
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The spell I taught her...</font>

130
00:08:37,130 --> 00:08:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've grown so much, Doux...</font>

131
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Your Majesty?!</font>

132
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember, Jahi?</font>

133
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:47,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first time you and Doux met...</font>

134
00:08:48,010 --> 00:08:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Doux could barely even walk.</font>

135
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're doing amazing, Doux!</font>

136
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is Your Majesty's...</font>

137
00:09:02,850 --> 00:09:07,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm, looks like you will also suffice 
as the next demon king's attendant.</font>

138
00:09:07,820 --> 00:09:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! B-But that's so sudden!</font>

139
00:09:11,490 --> 00:09:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the problem with that?</font>

140
00:09:13,540 --> 00:09:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've gotten used to being 
my attendant, haven't you?</font>

141
00:09:16,590 --> 00:09:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to support 
Doux as she grows, Jahi.</font>

142
00:09:20,950 --> 00:09:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Support her...</font>

143
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's right...</i></font>

144
00:09:24,930 --> 00:09:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At some point, I was 
concentrating so much</i></font>

145
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>on teaching 
that I had forgotten...</i></font>

146
00:09:28,370 --> 00:09:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it! I did it!</font>

147
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yay!</font>

148
00:09:30,890 --> 00:09:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lady Doux is growing at her 
own pace, as she should.</i></font>

149
00:09:35,140 --> 00:09:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that my other duty is to 
support her growth by her side.</i></font>

150
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She taught me lots of things I 
couldn't do. So I learned them,</font>

151
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now I can do lots of things.</font>

152
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's wonderful, Lady Doux.</font>

153
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when Doux conquers the world...</font>

154
00:09:54,350 --> 00:10:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux is going to teach everyone around 
the world things they can't do!</font>

155
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux is gonna conquer the world 
to help everyone who's in trouble.</font>

156
00:10:06,420 --> 00:10:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?!</font>

157
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You pulled that off brilliantly, Doux!</font>

158
00:10:11,610 --> 00:10:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so proud of you, Doux!</font>

159
00:10:13,210 --> 00:10:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How?!</font>

160
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She ruined everything with that last part!</font>

161
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can only conquer the world</font>

162
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by taking from others, oppressing 
them, and ruling over them!</font>

163
00:10:21,330 --> 00:10:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet Lady Doux...</font>

164
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be such a spoilsport.</font>

165
00:10:25,700 --> 00:10:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just look at that crowd 
and how excited they are!</font>

166
00:10:30,310 --> 00:10:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone is admiring how brave Doux looks.</font>

167
00:10:34,310 --> 00:10:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She couldn't possibly 
be any more successful.</font>

168
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

169
00:10:38,570 --> 00:10:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to be more honest with yourself.</font>

170
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just praised her a moment ago, 
saying, "That's wonderful, Lady Doux."</font>

171
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha—</font>

172
00:10:45,990 --> 00:10:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And while you were beaming.</font>

173
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

174
00:10:50,090 --> 00:10:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I-I...</font>

175
00:10:51,710 --> 00:10:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I take back what I said!</font>

176
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't get a big head over this!</font>

177
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just because you grew a <i>tiny</i> bit</font>

178
00:10:57,700 --> 00:10:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">doesn't change the fact that 
I have many things</font>

179
00:10:59,650 --> 00:11:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to teach you still!</font>

180
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

181
00:11:02,970 --> 00:11:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope you'll continue to 
be prepared, Lady Doux!</font>

182
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup!</font>

183
00:11:20,610 --> 00:11:21,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The demon world.</i></font>

184
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A chaotic world where all demons 
carry out all their evil deeds.</i></font>

185
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With his great power, the demon king 
set out to conquer all worlds.</i></font>

186
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

187
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The demon king suddenly 
stopped his conquest,</i></font>

188
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>letting a fleeting moment of 
peace to come to the world.</i></font>

189
00:11:41,650 --> 00:11:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the reason behind this decision...</i></font>

190
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There are only a few who 
know that the reason</i></font>

191
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>lies within the demon king's daughter.</i></font>

192
00:11:49,370 --> 00:11:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The heir to the demon king...</i></font>

193
00:11:51,730 --> 00:11:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her name is Doux.</i></font>

194
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So what about Doux made the evil demon 
king stop his plans to conquer the world?</i></font>

195
00:11:59,910 --> 00:12:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

196
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The reason...</i></font>

197
00:12:05,170 --> 00:12:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Welcome home, Papa!</font>

198
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:11,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Doux!</font>

199
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you a naughty little girl?</font>

200
00:12:15,330 --> 00:12:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help you carry your stuff, 'kay?</font>

201
00:12:18,770 --> 00:12:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're such a sweet child that 
cares so much for your father!</font>

202
00:12:25,430 --> 00:12:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The reason he stopped his conquest is...</i></font>

203
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Future Demon King Is Too Kind!!</i></font>

204
00:12:29,530 --> 00:12:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE FUTURE DEMON KING IS TOO KIND!!</font>

205
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, darling.</font>

206
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you already done 
with work for the day?</font>

207
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he is not.</font>

208
00:12:40,090 --> 00:12:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he wanted to play with Lady 
Doux and ran out of the office.</font>

209
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear...</font>

210
00:12:44,290 --> 00:12:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Dahaka, what did you 
and Doux play today?</font>

211
00:12:50,210 --> 00:12:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we actually weren't playing. 
Doux said she wanted to study.</font>

212
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Study?</font>

213
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to study spwells!</font>

214
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:01,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? Are you tired of your toys?</font>

215
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuh-uh.</font>

216
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I promised everyone at my recital!</font>

217
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be a great demon 
king like you, Papa!</font>

218
00:13:10,570 --> 00:13:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux...</font>

219
00:13:12,130 --> 00:13:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not only kind,
but you've grown so much!</font>

220
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm learning real hard! Just watch!</font>

221
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

222
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ubaaborunikka Tajaruuya Koyanyo!</font>

223
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This incantation! It's a 
language conversion spell?!</font>

224
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she trying to learn 
such a high-level spell?!</font>

225
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rumu...ri... Rumu...to ...ta...</font>

226
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is where I always get stuck...</font>

227
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux! You're amazing!</font>

228
00:13:43,590 --> 00:13:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were able to recite a 
long incantation this far!</font>

229
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! That's already amazing.</font>

230
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's hopeless.</i></font>

231
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ever since the Face Reveal 
Ceremony ended in a huge success,</i></font>

232
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:56,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His Majesty and Lady Dahaka are 
babying Lady Doux even more.</i></font>

233
00:13:56,810 --> 00:13:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jahi, I've made up my mind!</font>

234
00:13:58,200 --> 00:14:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! A-About what?</font>

235
00:14:00,830 --> 00:14:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since Doux has made significant progress 
in becoming the next demon king,</font>

236
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">her trial today will be to experience 
the demon king's duties!</font>

237
00:14:08,110 --> 00:14:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Duties!</font>

238
00:14:09,530 --> 00:14:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

239
00:14:11,990 --> 00:14:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph. I'll acknowledge the guts you had 
to sneak into the demon castle as spies.</font>

240
00:14:19,180 --> 00:14:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get moving!</font>

241
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You rebels!</font>

242
00:14:22,170 --> 00:14:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On your knees!</font>

243
00:14:24,700 --> 00:14:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, please 
punish these criminals.</font>

244
00:14:32,730 --> 00:14:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harrumph!</font>

245
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What's Lady Doux doing here?</font>

246
00:14:38,990 --> 00:14:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty apparently wanted her
to experience his duties</font>

247
00:14:41,370 --> 00:14:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to help her become the next demon king.</font>

248
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?!</font>

249
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:48,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As she said, my daughter Doux 
will be punishing you all today.</font>

250
00:14:48,730 --> 00:14:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup!</font>

251
00:14:49,410 --> 00:14:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

252
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:52,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch! Who do you think we are?</font>

253
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What could a little brat like her do?</font>

254
00:14:55,530 --> 00:14:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll make you pay!</font>

255
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This feels so comfy and nice.</font>

256
00:15:07,870 --> 00:15:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sleepy bye.</font>

257
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-She put them to bed?!</font>

258
00:15:13,110 --> 00:15:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is supposed to be a 
spell called Dark Spores</font>

259
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which rots away anything it touches but...</font>

260
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux, what is this?!</font>

261
00:15:21,510 --> 00:15:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, all of the prisoners are always 
sleeping on top of really hard rocks,</font>

262
00:15:26,090 --> 00:15:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I learned a spell to 
make really fluffy futons.</font>

263
00:15:29,430 --> 00:15:30,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

264
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:34,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is quite a brilliant spell itself.</font>

265
00:15:35,590 --> 00:15:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need you to at least try 
to scold her, Your Majesty!</font>

266
00:15:41,310 --> 00:15:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}STRATEGY MEETING</font>

267
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't accept this!</font>

268
00:15:45,310 --> 00:15:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had handled the southern expedition 
field mission up until now!</font>

269
00:15:49,190 --> 00:15:53,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I was put in charge of 
it because you're useless.</font>

270
00:15:53,990 --> 00:15:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The weaker they are, the louder they cry!</font>

271
00:15:55,570 --> 00:15:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Say that again!</font>

272
00:15:58,590 --> 00:16:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, stop that! All of you!</font>

273
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it gets this bad, the only 
way to shut them up is with force.</font>

274
00:16:05,450 --> 00:16:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring it on! Step outside!</font>

275
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have some tea.</font>

276
00:16:11,330 --> 00:16:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you...</font>

277
00:16:16,950 --> 00:16:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a gentle flavor...</font>

278
00:16:19,450 --> 00:16:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They calmed down somehow!</i></font>

279
00:16:21,220 --> 00:16:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You work so hard, Doux.</font>

280
00:16:23,580 --> 00:16:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Doux.</font>

281
00:16:25,340 --> 00:16:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's very delicious.</font>

282
00:16:26,970 --> 00:16:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup!</font>

283
00:16:29,980 --> 00:16:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let us continue the meeting.</font>

284
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regarding the various supplies needed 
on these expedition field missions...</font>

285
00:16:36,110 --> 00:16:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything else that you need 
other than what's already been discussed?</font>

286
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

287
00:16:40,490 --> 00:16:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! Uh, well, if you 
would then, Lady Doux...</font>

288
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many snacks can they take with them?</font>

289
00:16:46,890 --> 00:16:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can't bring any!</font>

290
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if they're going on field trips, 
it'd be more fun to bring snacks.</font>

291
00:16:52,370 --> 00:16:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're not field trips! They're 
expedition field missions!</font>

292
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we just make them field trips?</font>

293
00:16:57,060 --> 00:16:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, let's.</font>

294
00:16:58,750 --> 00:16:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's that.</font>

295
00:16:59,530 --> 00:17:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

296
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew this would happen.</i></font>

297
00:17:06,630 --> 00:17:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lady Doux's kindness makes everyone 
else around her kind and easygoing.</i></font>

298
00:17:06,970 --> 00:17:08,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yay!</font>

299
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And it's unstoppable.</i></font>

300
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's trouble, Your Majesty!</font>

301
00:17:18,990 --> 00:17:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the ends of the demon 
world, the Jet Black Forest.</i></font>

302
00:17:18,990 --> 00:17:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}JET BLACK FOREST</font>

303
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The child of... a giant?</font>

304
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

305
00:17:32,860 --> 00:17:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can't understand our words,</font>

306
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:37,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so even when we try to move 
him, he just won't budge.</font>

307
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The giants are great warriors, 
members of an ancient civilization,</font>

308
00:17:41,130 --> 00:17:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and are known for their 
unparalleled strength.</font>

309
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:46,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not surprising.</font>

310
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the bigger problem 
here is not their strength</font>

311
00:17:49,370 --> 00:17:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the fact that he 
doesn't understand us.</font>

312
00:17:51,450 --> 00:17:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My language conversion spell doesn't 
work on the giants' language.</font>

313
00:17:56,420 --> 00:17:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then maybe if we use a 
little bit of force...</font>

314
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just...</font>

315
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

316
00:18:04,410 --> 00:18:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux!</font>

317
00:18:05,450 --> 00:18:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay.</font>

318
00:18:08,830 --> 00:18:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The giant quieted down.</font>

319
00:18:11,250 --> 00:18:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa! I'll try that talky spell!</font>

320
00:18:15,710 --> 00:18:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, Doux. That spell 
doesn't work on giants...</font>

321
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

322
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux wants to try!</font>

323
00:18:28,170 --> 00:18:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well. Give it a try.</font>

324
00:18:30,210 --> 00:18:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Kay!</font>

325
00:18:33,380 --> 00:18:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty?</font>

326
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's believe in Doux's growth.</font>

327
00:18:41,730 --> 00:18:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ubaabarunikka Tajaruiya Koyanru...</font>

328
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rumuri... Rumuto... Iru... Iru...</font>

329
00:18:55,650 --> 00:18:56,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, uh...</font>

330
00:18:56,940 --> 00:18:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah!</font>

331
00:19:00,260 --> 00:19:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Irupapitto!</font>

332
00:19:07,760 --> 00:19:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

333
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, the spell is weak, but the 
range is quite impressive.</font>

334
00:19:13,330 --> 00:19:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This should...</font>

335
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it didn't work after all.</font>

336
00:19:18,860 --> 00:19:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

337
00:19:24,530 --> 00:19:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Doux, what are you....</font>

338
00:19:27,330 --> 00:19:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Lady Bug!</font>

339
00:19:30,040 --> 00:19:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er... Lady Doux! Now's not 
the time for catching bugs!</font>

340
00:19:33,450 --> 00:19:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That child is lost.</font>

341
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:38,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the bug spoke!</font>

342
00:19:39,290 --> 00:19:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This child was separated from the 
giants and got lost in the forest</font>

343
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while the giants were moving.</font>

344
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:48,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know because I was stuck on him.</font>

345
00:19:48,550 --> 00:19:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doux, is this...</font>

346
00:19:52,060 --> 00:19:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if the spell doesn't work on giants,</font>

347
00:19:54,950 --> 00:19:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd have everyone 
around here help!</font>

348
00:19:58,310 --> 00:20:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he's lost, let's all 
look for his parents!</font>

349
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I see...</font>

350
00:20:03,550 --> 00:20:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, who exactly is "everyone"?</font>

351
00:20:05,570 --> 00:20:07,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That giant came from the northeast.</font>

352
00:20:07,820 --> 00:20:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

353
00:20:10,320 --> 00:20:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-N-Now a tree's talking!</font>

354
00:20:13,180 --> 00:20:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

355
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And even the mushrooms!</font>

356
00:20:15,830 --> 00:20:18,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What in the world is going on?</font>

357
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps Doux's kindness and 
the fact that she knows</font>

358
00:20:22,410 --> 00:20:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she's going to be the next 
demon king made this happen.</font>

359
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is truly a method befitting Doux.</font>

360
00:20:30,940 --> 00:20:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Befitting Lady Doux...</font>

361
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Lady Bug! Mr. Tree! Thank you!</font>

362
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about it.</font>

363
00:20:38,810 --> 00:20:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problem.</font>

364
00:20:41,050 --> 00:20:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Mr. Giant.</font>

365
00:20:50,110 --> 00:20:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're all together, so it's okay!</font>

366
00:20:53,730 --> 00:20:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye!</font>

367
00:20:57,750 --> 00:20:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye!</font>

368
00:21:02,170 --> 00:21:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We made new friends again.</font>

369
00:21:05,250 --> 00:21:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

370
00:21:06,610 --> 00:21:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His Majesty is staying behind 
at their settlement</i></font>

371
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to work out an alliance with the giants.</i></font>

372
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure that Lady Doux's kindness will 
continue to affect those around her.</i></font>

373
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Demons do not need kindness.</i></font>

374
00:21:21,570 --> 00:21:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At least, that's what I 
thought until recently.</i></font>

375
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But now, there's a small part of 
me that wants to see just how much</i></font>

376
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lady Doux's kindness can change the world.</i></font>

377
00:21:34,450 --> 00:21:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you have fun again today?</font>

378
00:21:36,450 --> 00:21:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today was fun!</font>

379
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear that.</font>

380
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sister Jahi! Let's do another 
trial together tomorrow!</font>

381
00:21:48,770 --> 00:21:50,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course.</font>

382
00:21:51,010 --> 00:21:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am your attendant, after all.</font>

383
00:21:56,980 --> 00:22:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}"LET'S READ THE PICTURE BOOK"
LYRICS: KANATA NAKAMURA
 COMPOSITION AND ARRANGEMENT: NAOKI YANAGISAWA
SONG: DOUX</font>

384
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:08,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Teach me, teach me even more</i></font>

385
00:22:08,610 --> 00:22:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Cruel and inhumane things!</i></font>

386
00:22:11,450 --> 00:22:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cruel and inhumane.</font>

387
00:22:12,430 --> 00:22:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}These trials are super duper fun</i></font>

388
00:22:16,330 --> 00:22:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Doux can, Doux can do them all</i></font>

389
00:22:20,670 --> 00:22:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Steal all the mushrooms</i></font>

390
00:22:23,340 --> 00:22:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must shrewdly oppress!</font>

391
00:22:24,630 --> 00:22:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let's play and share everything!</i></font>

392
00:22:26,840 --> 00:22:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No sharing allowed!</font>

393
00:22:28,340 --> 00:22:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let's take someone we don't know
And become friends</i></font>

394
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You just know
So many things</i></font>

395
00:22:48,190 --> 00:22:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please teach me, please teach me
Big Sister Jahi</i></font>

396
00:22:55,910 --> 00:22:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Big Sister Jahi</i></font>

397
00:23:09,460 --> 00:23:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O Great Benevolent God, 
Lord Ahura Mazda...</font>

398
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you just say?</font>

399
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kindness and innocence 
that child possesses...</font>

400
00:23:18,650 --> 00:23:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fear the future where the 
demons use it for evil.</font>

401
00:23:23,470 --> 00:23:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She should not be in the demon world.</font>

402
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring her to heaven.</font>

403
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This child...</font>

404
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The daughter of the demon king, Doux.</font>

